<span class="postbody">Hi All,
<br />

<br />
Not sure how many of you are aware of this, but in the hard Watering Hole expedition the Discordling Hollower drops a decent robe with a tunic look!! Stats on it aren't the best, but they aren't bad for those of us that aren't raiding these days... I'm replacing my earthweave robe with it and popping a 40 hp augment on it. My guild went poof before we got to Xegony so I'm a happy camper!
<br />

<br />
Robe of Turmoil
<br />
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM  
<br />
Weight: 2.0 Size: LARGE 
<br />
Slot: CHEST  
<br />
AC: +25 Str: +8 Sta: +9 Cha: +9 Int: +9 Fire Resist: +8 Disease Resist: +8 Cold Resist: +8 Poison Resist: +8 HP: +90 Mana: +100  
<br />
Classes: Necromancer Enchanter Magician Wizard  
<br />
Races: All Races 
<br />
Slot 1: Type 7</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
